dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer provides an index map that can be used to locate individual scanned map sheets.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon shapefile is an index to 1:62,500 scale maps of North America, titled 'Joint maps of the international boundary between United States and Canada : from the Gulf of Georgia to the northwesternmost point of the Lake of the Woods.â€™ To create this index, footprints were generated using the fishnet tool, and metadata were supplied for the digitized paper maps by Stanford University Libraries. After the footprints were created, the shapefile was trimmed and labeled according to the sources.
